{"change_type":"edit_sae_code","command":"run","env_overrides":[{"key":"ARCHITECTURE","value":"shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu"}],"expected_win":"lower_objective","family_name":"shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu","family_stage":"prototype","hypothesis":"最终重构公式设为 x_hat = Σ_{i∈S_shared(h(x))} α_i^sh(h(x)) b_i^sh + Σ_{e∈E_pk(h(x))} Σ_{j∈S_e^τ(r_sh(x))} α_{e,j}(r_sh(x)) b_{e,j}，其中 h(x)=ReLU(Bx) 是低秩 shared bottleneck，{b_i^sh} 是静态 shared coarse 子库，r_sh(x)=x-Σ_i α_i^sh b_i^sh，{B_e} 是静态 PK-routed expert 子库，E_pk(·) 由 low-rank hidden 上的 left/right product-key 路由选出少量 experts，JumpReLU 只改变 expert 内局部 support。在线侧仍可直接导出到 LUTurbo/Lottable 的“shared coarse 子库查表 + PK expert 选择 + expert 子库查表 + 有限加权和 + 选择性补偿”流水线，不依赖动态字典，因此该 family 判定为直接兼容。本轮唯一主假设是：相对 r263 仅把 `ARCHITECTURE` 从 `product_key_expert_jumprelu` 切到新 family `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，保持 `K=32`、`EXPANSION_FACTOR=1`、`NUM_EXPERTS=1024`、`ACTIVE_EXPERTS=2`、`LATENTS_PER_EXPERT=56`、`STAGE1_RATIO=0.25`、`FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256`、`OPTIMIZER=adam`、`LR=8e-4` 与其余 recipe 不变，用廉价 low-rank shared coarse branch 替代 plain PK 的无 shared 主干，同时保留 full-expert PK cleanup，能够在 exact `total_cost_ratio=0.0816802978515625` 的近同成本档位比 r263/r266 更有效地压低 exceed_alpha_0.50，并形成更有价值的新 objective 点。","needs_sanity":true,"next_hypotheses":["如果该 family 在约 `0.08168x` 下明显优于 r263 并接近或击败 r266，下一轮应留在该 family，只改 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=32`，测试 shared bottleneck 是否还能进一步降 cost 而不明显抬高 exceed。","如果该 family 只比 plain PK 小幅更好但仍明显输给 incumbent，则记录为“shared low-rank coarse + PK cleanup` 有一定价值，但 shared coarse 的表达力仍不够”，后续不要在这条线做低信息细扫。","如果该 family 明显失败，则可更有把握地下调“shared low-rank coarse + PK cleanup”优先级，把预算转回其他真正改变 tail cleanup 语义的结构槽位。"],"notes_to_memory":["已实际落盘新 family `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu`，真实改动文件为 `sparsify/config.py`、`sparsify/sparse_coder.py`、`research/AutoResearch/override_registry.py`、`research/AutoResearch/prior_research_history.md`。","该 family 与 `shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 的精确差异是：always-on shared branch 从 full `d_in -> latents` sparse encoder 改为 low-rank bottleneck `h(x)=ReLU(Bx)` 上的 factorized shared coarse head；与 `shared_product_key_factorized_expert_topk` 的精确差异是：只有 shared coarse 与 PK routing 走低秩 hidden，routed expert cleanup 仍保留 full `d_in -> latents_per_expert` expert encoders，而不是 factorized expert heads。","为了避免继承自 reference 配置的 `FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM=256` 把成本抬回旧的高成本负信号区，本实现将 shared hidden 维度限制为 `min(FACTORIZED_HIDDEN_DIM, LATENTS_PER_EXPERT)`；在当前 recipe 下实际 hidden_dim=56。","exact-string smoke 已通过：`SparseCoderConfig(architecture='shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu', k=32, expansion_factor=1, stage1_ratio=0.25, factorized_hidden_dim=256, num_experts=1024, active_experts=2, latents_per_expert=56)` 可成功 instantiate、forward、backward。","本地 allowlist 校验已通过：`validate_env_overrides([{key:'ARCHITECTURE', value:'shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu'}], fallback_architecture='shared_product_key_expert_jumprelu')` 返回 `[]`。","本地 exact 成本复核：selection_accesses=178752 (`0.0426177978515625x`)、deployment_accesses=163840 (`0.0390625x`)、combined_accesses=342592 (`0.0816802978515625x`)；这比 dual-shared / lowrank-trunk 线更轻，几乎回到 plain PK 的成本档位。","兼容性注册表已补充该 family，当前解析结果为 `direct_compatible`；更新后本地计数为直接兼容 15 个、扩展兼容 25 个、不兼容 3 个。","在该 exact 成本档位，若想击败 r263 objective=0.27600582122802736，所需 exceed 门槛约为 `0.19432552337646484`；若想击败 incumbent r266 objective=0.275001，则所需 exceed 门槛约为 `0.1933207021484375`。"],"reference_round":263,"self_review":"这轮符合当前运行优先级。r274-r276 已经在 dual-shared scaffold 上连续给出不够强的 objective 信号，其中 r275 虽有正向 exceed 改善，但仍未接近 incumbent，而 r276 的 adaptive 变体又回退；按规则此时应优先换结构槽位，而不是继续在同一 scaffold 上做 split/active-path 邻域细扫。选择 `shared_lowrank_product_key_expert_jumprelu` 而不是继续堆 dual-shared 变体，是因为它更直接对应当前高优先级方向“shared bottleneck + expert-specific head”，同时保留当前已验证有效的 PK cleanup 语义，并且本地 exact cost 复核落在 `~0.08x`，明显优于 `shared_lowrank_*` 旧家族在当前 1024-expert recipe 下的 `~0.19x` 高成本负信号。代码侧只新增最小 family，并完成 whitelist、factory dispatch、override allowlist、compatibility registry 与 exact-string smoke；没有新增